# PORTFOLIO.md — Portfolio Manager Long-Term Memory

> Template. Copy to `PORTFOLIO.md` (gitignored) and fill in your own
> portfolios, accounts, and data source. The structure below is what
> the scheduled jobs (`warren-bot-fett-daily-market-scan.prompt`,
> `warren-bot-fett-ai-sleeve-monthly.prompt`) expect to find.

## Special-Case Portfolios (optional)

Use this section to document any portfolio with non-standard rules —
e.g. a trust with its own tax framework, beneficiary structure, or
investment-authority constraints. Skip if not applicable.

**Example placeholder:**

